window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For the first time in audio, the Cycle of Fire Trilogy, a stout and epic tale mixing Sci Fi and Fantasy by acclaimed author Janny Wurts. </p> <p> Book 3 Shadowfane:The concluding novel in the \"Cycle of Fire\" fantasy trilogy. Jaric inherits his father's powers, and as he struggles to successfully assume them, mankind's enemies are growing strong. </p> <p>Janny Wurts is the author of several fantasy series, and the internationally best selling Empire trilogy written in collaboration with Raymond E. Feist. She paints all her own covers depicting her vision of characters and setting. She is also an expert horsewoman, sailor, musician and archer.</p>"; 
